{"tid":815661,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我都幾擔心我老豆","createTime":"2018-09-12T08:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T14:56:06.000Z","uid":190283,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec886d8a404648982784459faa4918955c55b45","tid":815661,"uid":190283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:10:31.000Z","msg":"小妹我今年20出頭，呀媽係我小學嗰陣因爲生病唔係到。 <br />\n我同我細佬同老豆三個人一齊生活<br />\n雖然會慢慢習慣，我都知道我老豆都好大機會會再識過其他女人，始終男人都需要人照顧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我真係好擔心佢傻下傻下比女人搵笨都唔知。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴絲有差唔多經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我最近仲見佢日日wechat 如果係大陸女人我仲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f242f1cf62689af5d7058da356a9997c4006b7b","tid":815661,"uid":208726,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:12:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ded987776164a3db982615684d8f70190a006ea","tid":815661,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:14:26.000Z","msg":"無左間屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a206c0008c95668a9969656d5c1ed73dd596d0a0","tid":815661,"uid":190283,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0ded987776164a3db982615684d8f70190a006ea","tid":815661,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:14:26.000Z","msg":"無左間屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  今次真係爸爸唔好唔要我"},{"pid":"bbbae557b7d15526bae0a13aa30c140567c30bc3","tid":815661,"uid":114275,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:23:10.000Z","msg":"係老豆面前日日大聲朗讀蝗婦搶公屋